genresAdvancedInfo.name: arpa grande
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Arpa grande is a traditional music genre from Mexico that features the harp as the main instrument. It is often played in small ensembles and is characterized by intricate melodies, fast tempos, and virtuosic playing. The music is deeply rooted in Mexican culture and is often associated with celebrations and festivals.
